ecent seizures illustrating the vast scale of these illicit operations.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/myanmars-anti-drug-crackdown-authorities-torch-usd-600-million-worth-of-seized-narcotics/articleshow/132009997.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/myanmars-anti-drug-crackdown-authorities-torch-usd-600-million-worth-of-seized-narcotics/articleshow/132009997.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-26T12:58:25+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132010022,imgsize-228591.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Life-changing donation: Snapchat CEO Evan Spiegel and his wife Miranda Kerr donate $550 million to clear medical debt for more than 261,000 California residents]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132010204.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/life-changing-donation-snapchat-ceo-evan-spiegel-and-his-wife-miranda-kerr-help-erase-550-million-in-medical-debt-for-more-than-261000-california-residents/articleshow/132010204.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/life-changing-donation-snapchat-ceo-evan-spiegel-and-his-wife-miranda-kerr-help-erase-550-million-in-medical-debt-for-more-than-261000-california-residents/articleshow/132010204.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-26T13:05:56+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132010180,imgsize-764505.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Greece turns to space technology: AI-powered satellites begin tracking wildfires]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132009927.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Greece is pioneering a new defense against wildfires with a constellation of four compact satellites. These space-based eyes, equipped with thermal sensors, detect nascent blazes as small as four meters, providing crucial early warnings. Integrated with AI, the system prioritizes threats, enabling faster response and potentially saving lives and property amidst escalating fire seasons.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/greece-turns-to-space-technology-ai-powered-satellites-begin-tracking-wildfires/articleshow/132009927.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/greece-turns-to-space-technology-ai-powered-satellites-begin-tracking-wildfires/articleshow/132009927.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-26T12:53:52+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132009941,imgsize-54386.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Oprah Winfrey: "One of the things that I encourage for anybody who is interested in their own charity or philanthropy is…"]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132009954.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-oprah-winfrey-one-of-the-things-that-i-encourage-for-anybody-who-is-interested-in-their-own-charity-or-philanthropy-is/articleshow/132009954.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-oprah-winfrey-one-of-the-things-that-i-encourage-for-anybody-who-is-interested-in-their-own-charity-or-philanthropy-is/articleshow/132009954.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-26T12:53:59+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132009963,imgsize-1376103.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['America, meet your next federal budget director’: JD Vance jokes after Usha Vance buys $50 dress for $8.75]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132008348.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US Vice President JD Vance playfully nominated his wife, Usha Vance, as the next federal budget director after she highlighted a bargain maternity dress purchase. This followed a New York Times piece analyzing the 'political symbolism' of her pregnancy wardrobe. Usha Vance's witty response and the subsequent budget quip underscore the administration's focus on fiscal restraint and relatable, working-class economic messaging, despite Vance's past advocacy for American manufacturing.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/america-meet-your-next-federal-budget-director-jd-vance-jokes-after-usha-vance-buys-50-dress-for-8-75/articleshow/132008348.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/america-meet-your-next-federal-budget-director-jd-vance-jokes-after-usha-vance-buys-50-dress-for-8-75/articleshow/132008348.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-26T11:49:18+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132008865,imgsize-147523.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[MacKenzie Scott's $7 billion donations in 2025 accounted for one-third of America's largest charitable gifts]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132008560.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/mackenzie-scotts-7-billion-donations-in-2025-accounted-for-one-third-of-americas-largest-charitable-gifts/articleshow/132008560